类 OnActionStatusChangedEvent

  • java.lang.Object
    • cn.inbot.navigationlib.event.OnActionStatusChangedEvent

  • public class OnActionStatusChangedEvent
extends java.lang.Object

    Navigation action status changed event.

    机器人活动改变事件类。

    This event will be posted when the robot's action status changed.
    当导航状态变化时，会通过EventBus抛出此事件对象。

    Author : Inbot
    Create Date : 2020/01/13
    JDK version used : JDK1.8
    Version : V1.0.0
    Copyright ©2020 Inbot Technology Ltd. All rights reserved.
